import { Grid, Editors} from 'slickgrid-es6';
import data from '../stubs/sample_data';
import {requiredFieldValidator} from '../utilities/utils'
import {iCargoFormatter} from '../utilities/iCargo.formatters'


const columns = [
  // {id: 'travelId', name: 'Travel Id', field: 'travelId', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Date},
  {id: 'flight', name: 'Flight No', field: 'flight', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter},
  {id: 'flight', name: 'Flight Date', field: 'flight', cssClass: 'cell-title', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'segment', name: 'Segment From', field: 'segment', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'segment', name: 'Segment To', field: 'segment', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  
  {id: 'details', name: 'Flight Model', field: 'details', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Body Type', field: 'details', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Type', field: 'details', maxWidth: 100, minWidth: 80, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Start Time', field: 'details', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'End Time', field: 'details', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Status', field: 'details', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Additional Status', field: 'details', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'details', name: 'Time Status', field: 'details', maxWidth: 100, minWidth: 80, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  
  {id: 'weight', name: 'Weight %', field: 'weight', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'weight', name: 'Weight Value', field: 'weight', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },

  {id: 'volume', name: 'Volume %', field: 'volume', minWidth: 90, editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'volume', name: 'Volume Value', field: 'volume', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },

  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Position1', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Value1', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Position2', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Value2', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter }, 
  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Position3', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'uldPositions', name: 'ULD Value3', field: 'uldPositions', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'revenue', name: 'Revenue', field: 'revenue', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'revenue', name: 'Yeild', field: 'revenue', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'sr', name: 'SR', field: 'sr', editor: Editors.Text },
  {id: 'queuedBooking', name: 'Booking SR', field: 'queuedBooking', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter },
  {id: 'queuedBooking', name: 'volume', field: 'queuedBooking', editor: Editors.Text,formatter: iCargoFormatter }
];
const options = {
  enableCellNavigation: true,
  enableColumnReorder: true,
  forceFitColumns: !true,
  frozenColumn: 0,
  frozenRow: 1,
  editable: true,
  enableAddRow: true,
  asyncEditorLoading: false,
  autoEdit: false
};
export default () => new Grid("#iCargoSpreadSheet", data, columns, options);
